{"title":"永远年轻的笑容","authors":["荧光"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远年轻的笑容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荧光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用寻找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他总在微笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要天上的群星没有殒落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就不会消失那笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他如果活着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是５０岁了吧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，不，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要人们没有失去良知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不会忘记雷锋真正的年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他与天地的正气同在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与人生的希望同庚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人曾说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“雷锋叔叔不在了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实那时也在；只不过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时他敛起了笑容——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在“四害”横行时他是怒雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在精神污染中他是清风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最困难的时刻他是号声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用寻找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁都认得他的："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他融入昨日人们的记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又来自今天人们心中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在历史长河中洗漱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦然回眸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又迎着九十年代的晨风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍是那身干净的旧军服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有，一副依然年轻的笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用寻找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他无处无时不在——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要人们具有他那笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且发自心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那般纯正。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋［中国画］   李琦"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}